WITH filtered_data AS (
    SELECT 
        c.Segment, 
        ym.CustomerID, 
        ym.Consumption
    FROM 
        customers c
    INNER JOIN 
        yearmonth ym ON c.CustomerID = ym.CustomerID
    WHERE 
        c.Currency = 'CZK' 
        AND ym.Date BETWEEN '201301' AND '201312'
),
min_consumption_per_segment AS (
    SELECT 
        Segment, 
        MIN(Consumption) AS min_consumption
    FROM 
        filtered_data
    GROUP BY 
        Segment
),
annual_avg_consumption AS (
    SELECT 
        fd.Segment, 
        SUM(fd.Consumption) / COUNT(DISTINCT fd.CustomerID) AS annual_avg
    FROM 
        filtered_data fd
    INNER JOIN 
        min_consumption_per_segment mcs ON fd.Segment = mcs.Segment AND fd.Consumption = mcs.min_consumption
    GROUP BY 
        fd.Segment
)
SELECT 
    (SELECT annual_avg FROM annual_avg_consumption WHERE Segment = 'SME') - 
    (SELECT annual_avg FROM annual_avg_consumption WHERE Segment = 'LAM') AS diff_SME_LAM,
    (SELECT annual_avg FROM annual_avg_consumption WHERE Segment = 'LAM') - 
    (SELECT annual_avg FROM annual_avg_consumption WHERE Segment = 'KAM') AS diff_LAM_KAM,
    (SELECT annual_avg FROM annual_avg_consumption WHERE Segment = 'KAM') - 
    (SELECT annual_avg FROM annual_avg_consumption WHERE Segment = 'SME') AS diff_KAM_SME
;	----- bird -----	debit_card_specializing

WITH consumption_2012 AS (
    SELECT 
        c.Segment,
        SUM(y.Consumption) AS consumption_2012
    FROM 
        customers c
    INNER JOIN 
        yearmonth y ON c.CustomerID = y.CustomerID
    WHERE 
        c.Currency = 'EUR' AND 
        substr(y.Date, 1, 4) = '2012'
    GROUP BY 
        c.Segment
),
consumption_2013 AS (
    SELECT 
        c.Segment,
        SUM(y.Consumption) AS consumption_2013
    FROM 
        customers c
    INNER JOIN 
        yearmonth y ON c.CustomerID = y.CustomerID
    WHERE 
        c.Currency = 'EUR' AND 
        substr(y.Date, 1, 4) = '2013'
    GROUP BY 
        c.Segment
),
consumption_change AS (
    SELECT 
        c2012.Segment,
        (c2013.consumption_2013 - c2012.consumption_2012) AS increase,
        ((c2013.consumption_2013 - c2012.consumption_2012) / c2012.consumption_2012 * 100) AS percentage_increase
    FROM 
        consumption_2012 c2012
    INNER JOIN 
        consumption_2013 c2013 ON c2012.Segment = c2013.Segment
)
SELECT 
    (SELECT Segment FROM consumption_change ORDER BY percentage_increase DESC LIMIT 1) AS max_segment,
    (SELECT Segment FROM consumption_change ORDER BY percentage_increase ASC LIMIT 1) AS min_segment	----- bird -----	debit_card_specializing
